Enable 32-bit architecture support: sudo dpkg --add-architecture i386

Graphical Install
Double click on the .deb package to install using the graphical package manager.

Terminal Install
wget https://www.scootersoftware.com/bcompare-4.2.8.23479_amd64.deb
sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install gdebi-core
sudo gdebi bcompare-4.2.8.23479_amd64.deb

Terminal Uninstall
sudo apt-get remove bcompare
